From: Oleksandr Natalenko <oleksandr@natalenko.name>
Subject: [pf-curated-7.0] fixes: natalenko's stable-backport fixes batch

Re-cut from natalenko's pf-kernel branch fixes-7.0 (tip dde10a5a7771)
as a single bulk diff, restricted to the files this overlay's curation
kept on the 7.0 active slot. Source: codeberg.org/pf-kernel/linux.

Large fixes branch on 7.0 — natalenko cherry-picked many upstream/
linux-stable fixes that gentoo-sources hasn't yet pulled (7.0 is
recently released, stable backports are still settling). 152 files
across drivers/, fs/, mm/, kernel/, security/, io_uring/, tools/,
net/, block/, lib/, arch/x86/. Includes the kernel/fork.c overlap with
archlinux-7.0 (identical hunks).
---
