+ * triggers a denial that is NOT logged.
+ *
+ * Phase 2 (after TSYNC without LOG_SUBDOMAINS_OFF): the sibling stacks another
+ * domain and triggers a denial that IS logged, proving the muting was
+ * overridden.
+ */
